name: Twintails Jetpack II
description:
Twintails Jetpack 2 Version 1.0.0

This fan-made game features 39 Levels, unlockables, and a story set in a world where music was lost!

Things might still be a bit buggy as we try to fix the bugs and improve the experience!

Happy Miku Day 2023!!!
